title: The Time Eminem Got Sued By His Own Mother

media:group.media:title: The Time Eminem Got Sued By His Own Mother
media:group.media:description:
Eminem dissed his mother so bad, she sued him, and not for an insignificant amount either. Eminem's mom sued him for $10m, with the lawsuit eventually succeeding, although not for the amount that Debbie Mathers initially expected. This event had come after the time Eminem got sued by his childhood bully, marking just one of the many times Marshall Mathers got sued.

This is, The Time Eminem Got Sued By His Own Mother.
